        </div>

        <div class="span5 zoom">
           <p><img src="http://localhost:3000/assets/Milestones.png" class="img-circle" /></p>
          <h3 align="justify"  style="font-family: Pussycat, Algerian, Broadway, fantasy; color: #0bb0ff;"> Milestones could be defined as yet to be achieved thoughts in mind that would help one reach its true Goal. Once  accomplised it converts into a Goal.</h3>
       </div>
	   
      
      </div>
      <br/>
      <br/>
      <br/>
